    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality example that has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks, while the interior remains in 'as-new' condition with no signs of wear on the upholstery or carpets. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been garage-kept and maintained with an open checkbook. For a buyer seeking the finest possible example of this model, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade car that looks and drives exactly as it did when it first left the dealership.",
      "price": 48500.0,
